# Lab IPsec - VPN Site-to-Site


## Objectif
Configurer un tunnel VPN IPsec site-to-site entre R1 et R3
à travers le routeur R2 (simulant Internet).

## Configuration R1

### Étape 1 - ISAKMP Policy (Phase 1)
crypto isakmp policy 10
 encr aes
 hash sha
 authentication pre-share
 group 2

crypto isakmp key cisco123 address 10.1.2.1

### Étape 2 - IPsec Transform Set (Phase 2)
crypto ipsec transform-set TSET esp-aes esp-sha-hmac
 mode tunnel

### Étape 3 - ACL trafic intéressant
access-list 100 permit ip 192.168.1.0 0.0.0.255 192.168.2.0 0.0.0.255
access-list 100 permit ip 192.168.1.0 0.0.0.255 172.16.2.0 0.0.0.255
access-list 100 permit ip 172.16.1.0 0.0.0.255 192.168.2.0 0.0.0.255
access-list 100 permit ip 172.16.1.0 0.0.0.255 172.16.2.0 0.0.0.255

### Étape 4 - Crypto Map
crypto map CMAP 10 ipsec-isakmp
 set peer 10.1.2.1
 set transform-set TSET
 match address 100

### Étape 5 - Appliquer sur interface
interface Se0/0/0
 crypto map CMAP

## Configuration R3

### Étape 1 - ISAKMP Policy (Phase 1)
crypto isakmp policy 10
 encr aes
 hash sha
 authentication pre-share
 group 2

crypto isakmp key cisco123 address 10.1.1.1

### Étape 2 - IPsec Transform Set (Phase 2)
crypto ipsec transform-set TSET esp-aes esp-sha-hmac
 mode tunnel

### Étape 3 - ACL trafic intéressant
access-list 100 permit ip 192.168.2.0 0.0.0.255 192.168.1.0 0.0.0.255
access-list 100 permit ip 192.168.2.0 0.0.0.255 172.16.1.0 0.0.0.255
access-list 100 permit ip 172.16.2.0 0.0.0.255 192.168.1.0 0.0.0.255
access-list 100 permit ip 172.16.2.0 0.0.0.255 172.16.1.0 0.0.0.255

### Étape 4 - Crypto Map
crypto map CMAP 10 ipsec-isakmp
 set peer 10.1.1.1
 set transform-set TSET
 match address 100

### Étape 5 - Appliquer sur interface
interface Se0/0/1
 crypto map CMAP

## Configuration R2 (ISP - pas de crypto)
ip route 192.168.1.0 255.255.255.0 10.1.1.1
ip route 172.16.1.0 255.255.255.0 10.1.1.1
ip route 192.168.2.0 255.255.255.0 10.1.2.1
ip route 172.16.2.0 255.255.255.0 10.1.2.1

## Vérification
show crypto isakmp sa
show crypto ipsec sa
ping 192.168.2.1 source 192.168.1.1
ping 172.16.2.1 source 172.16.1.1
